41:07.943 --> 41:08.988
Mom?

41:09.118 --> 41:10.119
No. Uh...

41:10.250 --> 41:12.992
Are you alright?

41:13.122 --> 41:14.863
[Sighs] I have to go.

41:14.994 --> 41:16.125
Wait.

41:16.256 --> 41:18.171
I'm sorry.
You were right.

41:18.301 --> 41:20.434
I need to talk to David.
Can you --No.

41:20.565 --> 41:23.568
Maddie, please.
Listen, I can do it.

41:23.698 --> 41:25.047
I can cure the Flaw.

41:25.178 --> 41:27.267
I want to help your Dad.

41:27.397 --> 41:29.704
He's dead.

41:29.835 --> 41:31.489
What?

41:31.619 --> 41:33.186
David's gone.

41:33.316 --> 41:34.927
He used the last of his power
to send Laurie's --

41:35.057 --> 41:37.277
[Line disconnects]

41:42.108 --> 41:44.153
Hello?Maddie?

41:44.284 --> 41:45.111
Maddie?

41:45.241 --> 41:46.460
Network's down.

41:46.591 --> 41:47.505
Which one?

41:47.548 --> 41:48.723
All of them.

41:48.767 --> 41:50.551
The Internet's going dark
everywhere.

41:50.682 --> 41:52.727
We don't have much time.What do you mean?

41:52.858 --> 41:56.122
Until the world feels ready
to come back online.

41:56.252 --> 41:58.951
When the networks return,
so will the UIs, and --

41:59.081 --> 42:00.866
David Kim is gone.

42:00.996 --> 42:02.389
David Kim?

42:02.520 --> 42:04.783
He was...
the one person I could see

42:04.913 --> 42:07.394
